        "javadoc": "/**\n * Composes functions.\n * <p>\n * The functions in the argument list are composed sequentially, in the\n * given order.  For example, compose(f1,f2,f3) acts like f1(f2(f3(x))).</p>\n *\n * @param f List of functions.\n * @return the composite function.\n */\n",
